<rule xmlns="http://windup.jboss.org/schema/jboss-ruleset" id="technology-usage-web-01700">
            <when>
                <file filename="{*}swing{*}.jar"/>
            </when>
            <perform>
                <technology-identified name="Swing">
                    <tag name="View"/>
                    <tag name="Rich"/>
                    <tag name="Embedded"/>
                </technology-identified>
            </perform>
        </rule>
